            "description": "Mendaftarkan user baru.\n\n**Pre-request Script:** Auto-generate email unik dengan timestamp\n\n**Test Script:**\n- Validasi status 201\n- Validasi response structure\n- Auto-save JWT token ke environment\n- Auto-save user ID ke environment"
          },
